Day 11:
Step 0: Log in to the Azure Portal (https://portal.azure.com/).


______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


1. Assigned a Azure Policy:
Step 1: Search for Azure and navigate to to Policy.
Step 2: Search for ALLOWED LOCATIONS in
Step 3: Click on ASSIGN POLICY.
Step 4: Enter the following details:
       a. Scope
       b. Resource Group
       c. Policy Definitions: 
       d. Allowed Locations
       e. Name
       f. Description
Step 5: Go to paramenters and select "CENTRAL INDIA"
Step 6: Enter the CREATE button to create the POLICY.

--> For Testing the Policy, I created:

1. A Virtual Network with the same parameter I entered for the creation of Policy: Success

2. A Storage Account with different parameter (East US): Failure


